## Setting H2 Movement Speed ##
EditTag globals\globals.globals
## Spartan ##
SetField PlayerInformation[0].RunForward 2.25
SetField PlayerInformation[0].RunBackward 2
SetField PlayerInformation[0].RunSideways 2
SetField PlayerInformation[0].StunTimeRange 0 1.25
SetField PlayerInformation[0].FirstPersonIdleTimeRange 10 15
SetField PlayerInformation[0].FirstPersonSkipFraction 0.25
## Elite ##
SetField PlayerInformation[1].RunForward 2.25
SetField PlayerInformation[1].RunBackward 2
SetField PlayerInformation[1].RunSideways 2
SetField PlayerInformation[1].StunTimeRange 0 1.25
SetField PlayerInformation[1].FirstPersonIdleTimeRange 10 15
SetField PlayerInformation[1].FirstPersonSkipFraction 0.25
SaveTagChanges
Exit


